title: New doubt as N. Korea labels South 'incompetent'
text:
New doubt as N. Korea labels South 'incompetent' 5:25pm BST - 01:30
South Korea had offered to play as a mediator between the North and United States. But after months of easing tensions the prospects of talks are now in doubt again. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
